===Pronunciation===
ῥύομαι / rhuomai / rhoo'-om-ahee
===Etymology===

Middle voice of an obsolete verb, akin to [[ῥέω ]] {{GG|4482}} (through the idea of a current; compare [[ῥύσις]] {{GG|4511}}); 
===Verb===
to rush or draw (for oneself), that is, rescue: - deliver (-er).